In this, we upgrade our WebGIS application by adding interactive map visualization using Google Earth Engine and Leaflet.js.
Here we will display satellite imagery directly on a web map.

🔍 What you will learn:

How to display satellite data on a web map
Understanding RGB visualization (true color imagery)
Understanding NDVI visualization (vegetation health)
How Google Earth Engine generates tile layers
How to integrate those tiles into Leaflet maps
How frontend and backend connect for map rendering
